Word of mouth works well if you are an extrovert and have a lot of acquaintances to get the ball rolling. if you tend to keep to yourself and aren&#039;t that outgoing, it&#039;s more difficult to take advantage of this way to promote your writing. Still, you should promote it as many different ways as you can to find what&#039;s the most successful way for you.]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>In reply to <a href="https://wordcounter.net/blog/2014/04/07/1025_46-ways-to-promote-your-writing.html#comments/12687">Steve</a>.</p>
<p>Word of mouth works well if you are an extrovert and have a lot of acquaintances to get the ball rolling. if you tend to keep to yourself and aren&#8217;t that outgoing, it&#8217;s more difficult to take advantage of this way to promote your writing. Still, you should promote it as many different ways as you can to find what&#8217;s the most successful way for you.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
		
