					<description><![CDATA[Don&#039;t forget good old word of mouth. If you write things that people want to share with others, they will pass it on to others. Find those who like to share the good books that they have read and it can be a great way to promote your writing.]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Don&#8217;t forget good old word of mouth. If you write things that people want to share with others, they will pass it on to others. Find those who like to share the good books that they have read and it can be a great way to promote your writing.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
		
