Promoting my work is the most difficult part of being a writer for me. It&#039;s not writing the book, editing the book or anything that typically is considered difficult. Promotion is what gets me because I&#039;m an introvert at heart. This list is quite helpful for someone like me to find ways to promote that don&#039;t mean I have to be an extrovert in the process.]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>In reply to <a href="https://wordcounter.net/blog/2014/04/07/1025_46-ways-to-promote-your-writing.html#comments/932">Taryn</a>.</p>
<p>Promoting my work is the most difficult part of being a writer for me. It&#8217;s not writing the book, editing the book or anything that typically is considered difficult. Promotion is what gets me because I&#8217;m an introvert at heart. This list is quite helpful for someone like me to find ways to promote that don&#8217;t mean I have to be an extrovert in the process.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
		
