					<description><![CDATA[As a published writer, the one thing that they never tell you when you start off is the amount of promotion that you need to do. Writing is only half the battle. It&#039;s probably even less than half the battle. If you want to be a successful writer, you need to be a successful promoter. If you don&#039;t want to promote your writing, you&#039;re going to have a hard time becoming a successful writer.]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>As a published writer, the one thing that they never tell you when you start off is the amount of promotion that you need to do. Writing is only half the battle. It&#8217;s probably even less than half the battle. If you want to be a successful writer, you need to be a successful promoter. If you don&#8217;t want to promote your writing, you&#8217;re going to have a hard time becoming a successful writer.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
		
